                  <div id="content-header">
                                      <h1 class="title">About</h1>
                                                          </div> <!-- /#content-header -->
        
        <div id="content-area">
          <div class="node node-type-page" id="node-4"><div class="node-inner">

  
  
  
  
  
  <div class="content">
    <div id="about_text">
<p>
Peter A. Cole, Architect is a small, full service Architectural Design Firm specializing in high end residential design, both renovations/additions, and new construction. We strive to design our projects in harmony with the architectural and natural context into which they are to be built. As a LEED Accredited Professional, Mr. Cole endeavors to incorporate appropriate sustainable, environmentally responsible and energy efficient elements into our homes. </p>
<p>Our Clients enjoy significant personal attention from Mr. Cole both during the design and construction phases of their projects. Over the past 25 years we have completed over 300 projects, primarily in Westchester County, New York and Lower Fairfield County Connecticut. Other assignments have included vacation homes in Vermont, Massachusetts, Upstate New York and Florida.</p>
<p>Peter Cole, Principal of the firm, obtained his Master of Architecture Degree from Washington University in St. Louis and is an active member of the American Institute of Architects. Other staff are licensed Architects with a broad range of project experience from over 15 years with the firm.
</p>
</div>
  </div>

  
